		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Swarmhost barbarians have the unusual ability to transform themselves into a sentient swarm, most often a swarm of insects (like wasps), or inanimate material (like shards of glass), or viscous material (like magical shadow). While a swarmhost maintains a generally humanoid form, their rage causes their physical form to separate and whirl in midair.</em></p><table><caption><p>The Slayer</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Features</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.KdOd5aG9bm2AzLaD]{Gather Swarm}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.00AMzpkGsP57t10R]{Swarm Form}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.Pzg7wwV55ELWp5lA]{Whirling Form}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>6</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.6eUuxduBTAYs5izr]{Critical Mass}, Improved Swarm Form</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>10</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.o2ZzN41a2ytdUgZ3]{Disperse}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>14</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.WOc6j3P25h5ZXSIo]{Legion}</p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
